{"tid":297534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"因為我唔返教會，搞到就快分手","createTime":"2017-06-25T14:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T07:10:39.000Z","uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49dd432538c6836b8cbe6a850bb9998691e8afe0","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟女朋友就返教會，想叫埋我返<br />\n咁我就話睇下點啦，老母朝早約左我<br />\n咁我同老母食完lunch<br />\n就打比女朋友啦<br />\n佢就開始唔開心，話好想見我<br />\n咁我記得呢間教會1點就收皮<br />\n咁我就話唔去啦，去到又好快走<br />\n之後佢就開始嬲，咁我知大事不妙<br />\n所以就話我去啦<br />\n點知佢就話唔洗啦，唔想見你啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到宜家我已經做曬死狗咁<br />\n佢都話唔原諒我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴絲比下意見點樣氹佢"},{"pid":"d897076fbba8680e9161a5da081f5fca2bd9063d","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1925d825185cea98e0feff9a5a50ba0e9d82b95","tid":297534,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bb22571abddb1ea16c930d8e7bcb4d573b715e","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a07e4a47496d35a965ab5d2fc491aa21997b48","tid":297534,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"返得一次就好難走<br />\n班耶撚會熔左你"},{"pid":"410aa523d4f73bd7eedf7cfe7b8e186c86526c7f","tid":297534,"uid":117855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"樽鹽何在<br />\n<br />\n男人之恥 <br />\n<br />\n抵你死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"h