s/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0089e0476c2f5e762fe80e14e1c050812363f8","tid":297534,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"反而你要洗佢腦，日日同佢講教會啲衰嘢、聖經嘅破綻，等佢早啲脫離呢啲19教會同教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成功例子"},{"pid":"d13cdb2d945e37cdfd421d2e0f05c187a634788b","tid":297534,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"追耶西已經ON9, 做到老婆奴就仲ON9"},{"pid":"32452048b76a9befabe7e4fc23861f46f12a6e30","tid":297534,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"遲早都係咁先"},{"pid":"d62645ab945095d53e7ed3c9b8b73ea385983a05","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而你要洗佢腦，日日同佢講教會啲衰嘢、聖經嘅破綻，等佢早啲脫離呢啲19教會同教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成功例子</blockquote><br />\n試過，但佢都會得閒想返下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b40b251f76fa0067a01a232a31b52b139fa4ec","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"點氹好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b8d98bad50b922be70b353c3b04ac3f19ab98a","tid":297534,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>反而你要洗佢腦，日日同佢講教會啲衰嘢、聖經嘅破綻，等佢早啲脫離呢啲19教會同教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成功例子</blockquote><br />\n試過，但佢都會得閒想返下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用一年時間就搞掂哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾年冇再返過，大部分教友都斷絕聯絡，飯前祈禱都唔撚駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過亦都真係證明咗佢啲所謂小組教友幾虛偽，識咗成十年，平時扮到點fd咁，一冇返教會就完全冇理過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c888818608c50ca4cc1d5669e6394863a783760b","tid":297534,"uid":65605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而你要洗佢腦，日日同佢講教會啲衰嘢、聖經嘅破綻，等佢早啲脫離呢啲19教會同教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成功例子</blockquote><br />\n試過，但佢都會得閒想返下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用一年時間就搞掂哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾年冇再返過，大部分教友都斷絕聯絡，飯前祈禱都唔撚駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過亦都真係證明咗佢啲所謂小組教友幾虛偽，識咗成十年，平時扮到點fd咁，一冇返教會就完全冇理過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女朋友個間可能知我返去玩玩下，唔會wts煩我<br />\n但成日煩我條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6688fb4555b16b46bdc6ae53c70844b73587124","tid":297534,"uid":30800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>反而你要洗佢腦，日日同佢講教會啲衰嘢、聖經嘅破綻，等佢早啲脫離呢啲19教會同教友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：成功例子</blockquote><br />\n試過，但佢都會得閒想返下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用一年時間就搞掂哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾年冇再返過，大部分教友都斷絕聯絡，飯前祈禱都唔撚駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過亦都真係證明咗佢啲所謂小組教友幾虛偽，識咗成十年，平時扮到點fd咁，一冇返教會就完全冇理過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女朋友個間可能知我返去玩玩下，唔會wts煩我<br />\n但成日煩我條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地啲招數嚟，一開始唔返就係咁問佢做咩唔返，打溫情牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就喺佢地眼中直頭係魔鬼嚟，跟過佢返幾次小組活動，我就專登玩嘢係咁串鳩佢地又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p